# build output
dist/
# generated types
.astro/

# NOTE: src/paraglide/ is intentionally NOT ignored. The inlang/paraglide
# compiler fetches its message-format plugin over the network on each
# build, which fails inside agent sandboxes with restricted egress. We
# commit the compiled output so `astro build` works offline. See CLAUDE.md
# for the agent-facing rule.

